      *%METADATA                                                       *
      * %TEXT Recreate for PMR - dup key errmsg - OPM                  *
      *%EMETADATA                                                      *
     H* RECREATE FOR PMR - DUP KEY ERRMSG - OPM
     FAPSUMRY UP  E                    DISK                      A
     C*          1         CHAINAPSUMRY              99
     C* Create a duplicate key:
     C                     Z-ADD1         VNDRNO
     C                     Z-ADD26.98     INVTOT
     C                     WRITESUMMREC
     C*
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
